Task: 9b9gyE-sort-manual-chapters
==============================================================================

Motivation
----------
In order to generate the documentation in the correct order it is necessary to sort its chapters based on dependencies.

Goals
--------
Implement a mechanism for specifying dependencies between docs.md files.
Specify dependencies for all docs.md files.
Generate documentation according to the specified dependencies.


Test Plan
---------
The generated documentation will be inspected to make sure it conforms to the specified dependencies and that it is internally consistent and logical.
